        "description": "<p>When Prava the witch threatens Camelot, Merlin steps in to defend the kingdom in the best way possible... kart racing. <em>Merlin Racing</em> draws a lot from the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/6590/super-mario-kart/\">Super Mario Kart</a> school of kart racing, featuring cartoony characters and physics and weapons players can use to take each other out. This game is distinguished by having three different kinds of cars: traditional go karts, airboats, and spacecraft. There are 25 tracks total, split between the three different car types.</p>\n<p>In addition to an adventure mode, which features players proceeding through story-based missions to take out Prava, there is a basic arcade mode, a time trial mode, and a tournament mode.</p>",
